name: Send New Touch Of Fire In My Soul Lord
chorusText:
Send a new touch of fire in my soul Lord
Send it now Lord, send it now,
Touch my lips today with a burning coal,
Send a new touch of fire in my soul

Send a new touch of fire in my soul Lord
Send it now Lord, send it now,
Touch my lips tonight with a burning coal,
Send a new touch of fire in my soul
